  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK970">
<l>iḷivariṉ vāḻāta māṉa muṭaiyā </l>
<l>roḷitoḻu tēttu mulaku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The world will (always) praise and adore the fame of the honourable who would rather die than suffer indignity.</l>
            </lg>
